[2;36m                    [0m         [39m== libFuzzer crashing input ==[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA Java process running a fuzzing harness for PDF text extraction encountered an [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mout-of-memory condition. The fuzzer reported a `FuzzerSecurityIssueLow: Out of [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmemory` triggered by a `java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space`. The failure [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moriginates in the Apache FontBox PFB font parser when invoked through Apache [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPDFBox’s Type1 font handling and PDF text stripping code.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  While processing a specially crafted PDF input, the Java heap was exhausted, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcausing an `OutOfMemoryError`. The fuzzer output recommends using `-Xmx1710m` to [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreproduce the condition.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Vulnerability type  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Classified by the fuzzer as `FuzzerSecurityIssueLow` due to excessive memory [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconsumption.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key observations  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The immediate failure point is in `org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m166[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The call chain flows from PfbParser into `Type1Font.createWithPFB`, then [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrough `PDType1Font`, `PDFontFactory`, and into PDFBox’s content stream and text [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstripping modules [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`PDFStreamEngine`, `LegacyPDFStreamEngine`, `PDFTextStripper`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The harness entry point is [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`com.example.PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput`, which drives PDFBox’s text [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextraction API.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Code areas for investigation  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Apache FontBox: `PfbParser.parsePfb` and related PFB parsing routines.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Apache PDFBox font handling: `Type1Font`, `PDType1Font`, and `PDFontFactory`.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • PDF content processing and memory usage in `PDResources`, `PDFStreamEngine`, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand `PDFTextStripper`.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Fuzzing harness in `com.example.PDFExtractTextFuzzer` to understand how inputs [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreach the parser.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis evaluation highlights the memory exhaustion path in font parsing and PDF text [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstripping without speculating on root causes or remediation strategies.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m== libFuzzer crashing input ==[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe codebase’s PDF font parser [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPfbParser[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is triggering a Java heap-space [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mOutOfMemoryError when processing a PFB font segment. The attempted patch solely [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madds an explicit long suffix [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`L`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to the `MAX_LENGTH` constant [0m[1;39m([0m[39m100_000_000 → [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m100_000_000L[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in PfbParser, without altering its value or adding any checks. After [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapplying this change, the same OutOfMemoryError still occurs at [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PfbParser.parsePfb`, indicating that the patch did not affect the underlying [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39missue.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A Jazzer fuzzing session reports:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `com.code_intelligence.jazzer.api.FuzzerSecurityIssueLow: Out of memory`[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Root cause: `java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space`[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Stack trace pinpoints allocation in [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb`, called during PDF text extraction via [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDFTextStripper.getText`.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Observation: The parser attempts to buffer an entire PFB font segment in memory, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mleading to excessive heap usage for large or malicious inputs.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Location: `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.java`[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Original code excerpt:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    private static final long MAX_LENGTH = 100_000_000;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Patched code excerpt:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    private static final long MAX_LENGTH = 100_000_000L;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Comments updated to clarify “Maximum allowed PFB payload to buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmitigate OOME.”[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No additional logic was introduced to enforce or check `MAX_LENGTH` at parse [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtime.[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Result  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After rebuilding with the patch, the same OutOfMemoryError recurs in [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PfbParser.parsePfb` when invoked by `Type1Font.createWithPFB` and downstream PDF [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocessing.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The log and stack trace are identical, confirming that changing the numeric [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mliteral suffix had no impact on buffering behavior or memory management.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- PfbParser.parsePfb: examine how payload lengths are read, validated, and whether [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe `MAX_LENGTH` constant is ever enforced during parsing.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Buffer allocation logic: identify calls to byte-array or stream buffering that [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmay allocate more than the intended cap.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Type1Font.createWithPFB: trace how parsed data flows into font construction and [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhether intermediate structures amplify memory usage.  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Overall PDFBox font loading path: review any lazy-loading or streaming [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malternatives that could replace full in-memory buffers.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mjava.base/java.lang.invoke.LambdaForm$MH/[0m[1;35m0x0000000800cb8c00.invoke_MT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLambdaForm$MH[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m)[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDEDUP_TOKEN: 4fc18e0e0662428e[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m== libFuzzer crashing input ==[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA Java‐based PDF font parser [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPfbParser[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m repeatedly triggers an OutOfMemoryError [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhen fed a fuzzed PFB stream. The initial failure occurs in `PfbParser.parsePfb`, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mas the parser eagerly loads the entire PFB payload into memory via [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mInputStream.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. A patch was applied to replace the unbounded [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mreadAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call with a buffered read into a `ByteArrayOutputStream`, tracking[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe total bytes read and aborting if a new constant `MAX_LENGTH` is exceeded. [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDespite this change, the same heap‐space exception still arises in `parsePfb` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnow [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mone line later[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, indicating that the patch did not prevent unbounded memory [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocation during parsing.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer reports a low‐severity security issue due to an `OutOfMemoryError: [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJava heap space`.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Stack trace points to [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35morg.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:166[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` as the origin.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The error surfaces when parsing a crafted PFB stream through the fuzzer harness [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The test logs recommend using `-Xmx1710m` to reproduce the failure.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mImportant observations  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The constructor of `PfbParser` originally invoked `[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, which [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocates a byte array sized to the entire input.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Very large or malicious payloads exhaust the Java heap before any downstream [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing logic runs.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The failure always occurs in `parsePfb`, not in any downstream PDFBox text [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextraction routines.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `PfbParser.java`, the constructor was rewritten to:  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Import `java.io.ByteArrayOutputStream`.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Read the input stream in [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m KB chunks into a `ByteArrayOutputStream`.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Maintain a `long total` count of bytes read.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • If `total` exceeds `MAX_LENGTH`, throw `[0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"PFB payload too large: "[0m[39m +[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotal[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • After reading completes, obtain a byte array via `[0m[1;35mbaos.toByteArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and pass [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mit to `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The diff context:  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```diff[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  --- a/fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.java[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  +++ b/fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.java[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  @@ [0m[1;36m-20[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m +[0m[1;36m20[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m7[0m[39m @@[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   import java.io.IOException;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   import java.io.InputStream;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  +import java.io.ByteArrayOutputStream;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[33m...[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  @@ [0m[1;36m-100[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m9[0m[39m +[0m[1;36m101[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m19[0m[39m @@[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   -    public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal InputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   -    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   -        byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +    public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal InputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +        ByteArrayOutputStream baos = new [0m[1;35mByteArrayOutputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +        byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m buf = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m8192[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +        int len;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +        long total = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +        while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mlen = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuf[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +            total += len;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtotal > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +                throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"PFB payload too large: "[0m[39m + total[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +            [0m[1;35mbaos.write[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuf, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, len[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +        byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35mbaos.toByteArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mResult after the patch  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer log shows the same `OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space`, now occurring [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mat `[0m[1;35mPfbParser.parsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:177[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The stack trace remains effectively identical beyond the incremented line number.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The patch does not prevent excessive memory allocation inside `parsePfb`, which [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstill creates large internal buffers or data structures.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for further investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The implementation of `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` itself—its internal buffering strategy, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocation patterns, and segment‐handling logic.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The value and placement of the `MAX_LENGTH` constant, including whether it is [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mactually enforced before large allocations occur downstream.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Any other code paths in `PfbParser` that allocate large arrays or collections [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbased on the payload size.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPDFBox font or resource factories, to identify additional in‐memory accumulations.[0m  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvery large memory allocations during font parsing.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Important Observations  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The OOM occurs before returning from the PfbParser constructor, indicating [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat the problematic code is within `parsePfb`.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The crash reproduces consistently, and increasing the heap [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. via [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`-Xmx1710m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m merely delays but does not prevent the failure.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No other errors or exceptions precede the heap exhaustion, pointing to [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muncontrolled buffering or array growth in the parser logic.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A guard was inserted at the start of the `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructor:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes.length > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"PFB payload too large: "[0m[39m + bytes.length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This change aims to reject oversized inputs early and avoid calling [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on payloads exceeding `MAX_LENGTH`.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Log After Patch  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The patched code still produces:[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     Caused by: java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         at [0m[1;35morg.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:168[0m[1;39m)[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         at org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.<init>[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:118[0m[1;39m)[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[33m...[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The exception is still thrown inside `parsePfb`, confirming the new length [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcheck did not intercept the problematic input before memory exhaustion.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The implementation of `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, particularly how it reads and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffers sections of the PFB file, to identify unbounded allocations.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The value and placement of `MAX_LENGTH`: verify it matches all entry points [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand that alternative constructors or helper methods do not bypass the check.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any lazy-loading or multi-stage parsing within FontBox’s PFB handling that [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmight consume large heaps despite initial length checks.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Downstream use of the parsed data in `Type1Font.createWithPFB` and [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDType1Font` to see if additional buffers are allocated post-parse.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer harness `PDFExtractTextFuzzer` to map exactly how the raw bytes [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreach PfbParser and confirm there are no other code paths bypassing the patched [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstructor.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m---[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis report captures the observed behavior before and after the patch, highlights [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat the memory check did not stop the OOM, and identifies key code regions for [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfurther review.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`readLimitedBytes`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m enforcing a `MAX_LENGTH` cap and adjusts segment‐size parsing [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto use safe [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m-bit arithmetic and bounds checks. After applying the patch, the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuild fails with a compilation error in `PfbParser.java` at line [0m[1;36m103[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39m“’;’ [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexpected”[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, indicating a syntax mistake introduced during the refactoring.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A libFuzzer run against `PDFExtractTextFuzzer` exposed an unhandled [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlarge‐payload scenario in `org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb`, causing a [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space`.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The stack trace shows the error originates from `PfbParser.parsePfb` [0m[1;39m([0m[39minvoked [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvia `PDType1Font` → `PDFontFactory` → `PDFTextStripper`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, indicating that extremely[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlarge or malicious PFB data can exhaust the heap when loaded entirely.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Observations from the Initial Issue  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The constructor `[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` uses `[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, which [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munconditionally allocates based on input size.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No checks or limits are in place for very large or crafted PFB files, allowing[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzer input to drive heap exhaustion.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The exception is classified as FuzzerSecurityIssueLow but still represents a [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstability/resource denial issue.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Introduced an import for `ByteArrayOutputStream`.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added a new private helper `[0m[1;35mreadLimitedBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` that:  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Reads input in [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m KB chunks  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Tracks cumulative byte count in a `long total`  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Throws `IOException` if `total` exceeds `MAX_LENGTH`  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Modified constructors:  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString filename[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` now calls [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mthis[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mreadLimitedBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mFiles.newInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mPaths.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfilename[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` now calls `[0m[1;35mthis[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mreadLimitedBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[39min[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the byte‐array constructor, added a guard that throws if `bytes.length > [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_LENGTH`.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Updated the `parsePfb` loop to read segment sizes into a `long rawSize`, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidate it [0m[1;39m([0m[39m≥[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m and ≤ MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, update cumulative `total`, cast to `int`, and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthen read exactly that many bytes.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Patch Result  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Build output reports a single compilation error:  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     `[0m[35m/src/.../[0m[95mPfbParser.java[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m103[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m62[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[32m';'[0m[39m expected`  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This indicates a syntax issue around line [0m[1;36m103[0m[39m character [0m[1;36m62[0m[39m—most likely a [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmissing semicolon, brace, or mismatched parenthesis in the newly inserted code.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Because of this error, the `fontbox` module fails to compile, aborting the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreactor build.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Review the modified section around line [0m[1;36m103[0m[39m in `PfbParser.java` for syntax [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mirregularities [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., missing `;`, misplaced braces in the new `readLimitedBytes` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethod or constructor signatures[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Verify the definitions and accessibility of the `MAX_LENGTH` and [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PFB_[0m[1;33mHEAD[0m[39mER_LENGTH` constants in the class.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure the new helper method’s signature and its usage in constructors align [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrectly [0m[1;39m([0m[39mproper checked exceptions, matching parentheses[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Audit related font‐loading code [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `Type1Font.createWithPFB`, [0m             [2m                [0m
